# 🏬 Superstore Sales Analysis Dashboard (Power BI)

This Power BI dashboard analyzes sales performance of a retail superstore across multiple regions and categories. It highlights key metrics like revenue, profit, shipping performance, and customer segmentation.

## 📊 Key Features
- Regional Sales and Profit breakdown
- Category and Sub-Category performance
- Top 10 Customers by Sales & Profit
- Ship Mode and Order Priority analysis
- Interactive filters by Region, Category, and Date

## 📁 Files Included
- `Superstore_Sales.pbix` – The main Power BI report file
- `superstore_data.xlsx` – Dataset used for the analysis
- `dashboard_preview.png` – Screenshot of the dashboard

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX (for dynamic KPIs and calculated measures)
- Power Query (for cleaning and transforming data)

